<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>SERGURIGH – Servicio Integral de Seguridad e Higiene</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --teal: #1e8a9a;
      --teal-dark: #136070;
      --navy: #0b2d36;
      --gold: #d4a843;
      --gold-light: #e8c06a;
      --cream: #f2ede6;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --gray: #9ab4bc;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--cream);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════
       HERO / FONDO
    ═══════════════════════════════ */
    .hero-section {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* imagen de fondo */
    .hero-bg-img {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url('fondo.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }
    /* overlay oscuro sobre la imagen */
    .hero-bg-img::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(
        to bottom,
        rgba(11,45,54,0.78) 0%,
        rgba(11,45,54,0.65) 40%,
        rgba(11,45,54,0.90) 75%,
        rgba(11,45,54,1.00) 100%
      );
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-logo {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 3px solid rgba(212,168,67,0.6);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(30,138,154,0.15), 0 0 60px rgba(30,138,154,0.3);
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s .1s forwards;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: .85rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: .3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s .25s forwards;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 8rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: .9;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .03em;
      color: var(--white);
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s .4s forwards;
    }
    .hero-title span { color: var(--teal); }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gray);
      margin-top: .5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s .55s forwards;
    }

    .hero-desc {
      max-width: 580px;
      margin: 1.8rem auto 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(242,237,230,0.85);
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s .7s forwards;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s .85s forwards;
    }
    .btn-gold {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--navy);
      padding: .85rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      font-size: .95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: all .25s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(212,168,67,.4);
    }
    .btn-gold:hover { background: var(--gold-light); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(212,168,67,.5); }
    .btn-outline {
      border: 2px solid rgba(30,138,154,.7);
      color: var(--teal);
      padding: .85rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 3rem;
      font-size: .95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: all .25s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(30,138,154,.1); transform: translateY(-2px); border-color: var(--teal); }

    /* scroll flecha */
    .scroll-arrow {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2.5rem;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .3rem;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: .7rem;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeDown .7s 1.1s forwards;
    }
    .scroll-arrow svg { animation: bounce 1.8s infinite; }
    @keyframes bounce { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(6px)} }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════
       TABS NAV
    ═══════════════════════════════ */
    .tabs-wrapper {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: rgba(11,45,54,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,0.2);
    }
    .tabs-nav {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0;
      overflow-x: auto;
      scrollbar-width: none;
    }
    .tabs-nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

    .tab-btn {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.6rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      position: relative;
      transition: color .25s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .tab-btn::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 50%;
      right: 50%;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), var(--gold));
      border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;
      transition: left .25s, right .25s;
    }
    .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--cream); }
    .tab-btn.active { color: var(--white); }
    .tab-btn.active::after { left: 12px; right: 12px; }

    /* ═══════════════════════════════
       PANELS
    ═══════════════════════════════ */
    .panels-container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 5rem; }

    .panel { display: none; padding-top: 4rem; }
    .panel.active { display: block; animation: panelIn .4s ease; }
    @keyframes panelIn { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }

    /* section header */
    .panel-label {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: .5rem;
    }
    .panel-title {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .panel-title span { color: var(--teal); }
    .gold-line {
      width: 55px;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--teal), var(--gold));
      border-radius: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* ── QUIÉNES SOMOS ── */
    .quienes-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .photo-col { position: relative; }
    .profile-photo {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 2px solid rgba(30,138,154,.3);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.5), 0 0 40px rgba(30,138,154,.12);
      display: block;
    }
    .photo-badge {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -1rem;
      right: -1rem;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--navy);
      border-radius: .9rem;
      padding: .65rem 1.1rem;
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: .85rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(212,168,67,.4);
    }
    .info-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .bio-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.2);
      border-radius: 1.2rem;
      padding: 1.8rem;
    }
    .bio-card p { font-size: .97rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .bio-card p:last-child { margin: 0; }

    .block-title {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: .7rem;
    }
    .pills { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .45rem; }
    .pill {
      background: rgba(30,138,154,.14);
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.28);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      padding: .3rem .85rem;
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: var(--cream);
    }
    .mats { display: flex; gap: .8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .mat {
      background: rgba(212,168,67,.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.3);
      border-radius: .6rem;
      padding: .38rem .8rem;
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    @media(max-width:680px){ .quienes-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr} .photo-badge{right:.5rem;bottom:.5rem} }

    /* ── MISIÓN/VISIÓN ── */
    .mv-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.8rem;
    }
    .mv-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.2);
      border-radius: 1.4rem;
      padding: 2.2rem;
      transition: border-color .25s, transform .25s;
    }
    .mv-card:hover { border-color: var(--teal); transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .mv-icon { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .mv-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: .85rem;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
    }
    .mv-card p { font-size: .94rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: .7rem; }
    .mv-card p:last-child { margin: 0; }
    @media(max-width:600px){ .mv-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    /* ── SERVICIOS ── */
    .serv-filter { display: flex; gap: .6rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .sf-btn {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(30,138,154,.2);
      color: var(--gray);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      padding: .45rem 1.1rem;
      font-size: .82rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .2s;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    .sf-btn:hover, .sf-btn.on { background: var(--teal); border-color: var(--teal); color: var(--white); }

    .serv-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(270px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.4rem;
    }
    .serv-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.18);
      border-radius: 1.3rem;
      padding: 1.8rem;
      transition: transform .25s, border-color .25s, box-shadow .25s;
    }
    .serv-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--teal); box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(30,138,154,.18); }
    .serv-card.hide { display: none; }
    .s-icon {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      width: 50px; height: 50px;
      background: rgba(30,138,154,.14);
      border-radius: 11px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: .9rem;
    }
    .serv-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: .5rem;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }
    .serv-card p { font-size: .87rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--gray); }
    .s-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(212,168,67,.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(212,168,67,.25);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: .18rem .65rem;
      font-size: .72rem;
      color: var(--gold-light);
      margin-top: .75rem;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── CONTACTO ── */
    .contact-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .cinfo { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }
    .citem {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: .9rem;
      padding: 1.1rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.15);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .citem:hover { border-color: var(--teal); transform: translateX(4px); }
    .c-ico {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      min-width: 40px; height: 40px;
      background: rgba(30,138,154,.15);
      border-radius: 9px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    }
    .c-body strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: .7rem;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: .15rem;
    }
    .c-body span { font-size: .92rem; color: var(--cream); }

    .social-row { display: flex; gap: .7rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: .3rem; }
    .soc {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .4rem;
      padding: .5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 2rem;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1.5px solid;
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    .soc.wa{border-color:#25D366;color:#25D366}.soc.wa:hover{background:#25D366;color:#fff}
    .soc.fb{border-color:#1877F2;color:#1877F2}.soc.fb:hover{background:#1877F2;color:#fff}
    .soc.ig{border-color:#E1306C;color:#E1306C}.soc.ig:hover{background:#E1306C;color:#fff}
    .soc.li{border-color:#0A66C2;color:#0A66C2}.soc.li:hover{background:#0A66C2;color:#fff}

    /* FORM */
    .cform { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .frow { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .fg { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .35rem; }
    .fg label { font-size: .76rem; letter-spacing: .08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); }
    .fg input, .fg textarea, .fg select {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(30,138,154,.22);
      border-radius: .7rem;
      padding: .78rem 1rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: .92rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      resize: none;
    }
    .fg input:focus, .fg textarea:focus, .fg select:focus {
      border-color: var(--teal);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(30,138,154,.14);
    }
    .fg select option { background: var(--navy); }
    .fg input::placeholder, .fg textarea::placeholder { color: rgba(154,180,188,.5); }

    .submit-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--teal-dark) 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 2.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 2.2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
      transition: all .25s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(30,138,154,.35);
    }
    .submit-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(30,138,154,.45); }

    .success-msg {
      display: none;
      background: rgba(30,138,154,.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.35);
      border-radius: .9rem;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem;
      font-size: .93rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media(max-width:660px){ .contact-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2.5rem} .frow{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(30,138,154,.12);
      padding: 1.8rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: var(--gray);
    }
    footer a { color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

    /* FLOATING WA */
    .wa-float {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 1.8rem;
      right: 1.8rem;
      z-index: 200;
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #25D366;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(37,211,102,.5);
      animation: waPulse 2.8s infinite;
      transition: transform .2s;
    }
    .wa-float:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }
    @keyframes waPulse {
      0%,100%{ box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(37,211,102,.5); }
      50%{ box-shadow: 0 4px 28px rgba(37,211,102,.75), 0 0 0 7px rgba(37,211,102,.12); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════════ HERO ══════════════ -->
<section class="hero-section" id="inicio">
  <div class="hero-bg-img"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <img src="logo.jpg" alt="SERGURIGH" class="hero-logo"/>
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Villa Paranacito, Entre Ríos · Disponibilidad nacional</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">SERGU<span>RIGH</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">Servicio Integral de Seguridad e Higiene</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">Acompañamos a las organizaciones en la construcción de entornos de trabajo seguros, saludables y eficientes. Prevención, gestión de riesgos y cumplimiento normativo.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#" class="btn-gold" onclick="openTab('servicios');return false;">🛡️ Ver Servicios</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-outline" onclick="openTab('contacto');return false;">📩 Contactar</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-arrow" onclick="document.querySelector('.tabs-wrapper').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
    <span>ver más</span>
    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════ TABS ══════════════ -->
<div class="tabs-wrapper">
  <nav class="tabs-nav">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="openTab('quienes')">Quiénes Somos</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('misionvision')">Misión &amp; Visión</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('servicios')">Servicios</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="openTab('contacto')">Contacto</button>
  </nav>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════ PANELS ══════════════ -->
<div class="panels-container">

  <!-- ── QUIÉNES SOMOS ── -->
  <div class="panel active" id="panel-quienes">
    <p class="panel-label">La empresa</p>
    <h2 class="panel-title">¿Qué es <span>Sergurigh?</span></h2>
    <div class="gold-line"></div>

    <div class="quienes-grid">
      <div class="photo-col">
        <img src="romina.png" alt="Romina Calvo – Lic. Higiene y Seguridad" class="profile-photo"/>
        <div class="photo-badge">Lic. Higiene &amp; Seguridad</div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-col">
        <div class="bio-card">
          <p><strong>Sergurigh</strong> es una empresa de servicios integrales en Higiene y Seguridad Laboral orientada a distintos rubros e industrias, con el objetivo de acompañar a las organizaciones en la construcción de entornos de trabajo seguros, saludables y eficientes.</p>
          <p>Nuestro enfoque no se limita al cumplimiento normativo, sino que busca la <strong>mejora continua</strong> de los sistemas de prevención, promoviendo una cultura de seguridad sólida, sostenible y adaptada a las exigencias actuales del mundo laboral.</p>
          <p>Liderada por <strong>Romina Juliana Calvo</strong>, Técnica Universitaria en Higiene y Seguridad (UTN) con matrícula habilitada en Buenos Aires y Entre Ríos, y actualmente finalizando la Licenciatura en la misma disciplina.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <p class="block-title">Aptitudes clave</p>
